OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FA Cumbrian woman says she has been
OL,8,Fleft "devastated" after being served
OL,9,Fwith an eviction notice just days
OL,10,Fbefore new laws giving renters more
OL,11,Frights came into force.
OL,13,FAmanda Harrison was served with the
OL,14,Feviction notice on 27 April 2026 ahead
OL,15,Fof the Renters Right Act 2026 being
OL,16,Fintroduced.
OL,18,FChanges include the abolishment of
OL,19,FSection 21 "no fault" evictions which
OL,20,Fintroduces stronger rights for tenants.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
