OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FAmanda Harrison says she notified her
OL,8,Flandlord, Holker Estates, about mould
OL,9,Fand damp issues in her property but
OL,10,Fshe says that no action has been taken.
OL,12,FSpeaking to ITV Border, she said: "You
OL,13,Fcan see the plaster has come off over
OL,14,Fhere on the corner. The plaster came
OL,15,Foff in January last year and I had to
OL,16,Ftake the radiator off.
OL,18,F"I was absolutely in shock, I was
OL,19,Fdevastated, terrified, alone but it
OL,20,Fjust seems like they have a business
OL,21,Fplan and are sticking to it."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FIn a statement Holker Estates said:
OL,8,F"As Holker Estate continues to deliver
OL,9,Fits long-term vision for the Land and
OL,10,FProperty portfolio, some difficult
OL,11,Fdecisions have been necessary
OL,12,Fregarding the occupation of parts of
OL,13,Fthe residential estate.
OL,15,F"We fully recognise the impact these
OL,16,Fchanges may have and are working
OL,17,Fclosely with those affected to support
OL,18,Fthem through this transition.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,F"While we do not comment on individual
OL,8,Ftenancy matters, we remain committed
OL,9,Fto maintaining constructive
OL,10,Frelationships with all our tenants and
OL,11,Fto managing the Estate in a way that
OL,12,Fsupports its long-term sustainability.
OL,14,F"We have recently carried out a full
OL,15,Finspection of our residential estate,
OL,16,Fand we are currently progressing an
OL,17,Fextensive programme of property
OL,18,Fimprovements across our residential
OL,19,Fportfolio."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FRenters will now have more flexibility
OL,8,Fwith fixed contracts abolished and
OL,9,Ffairer rent rules in place.
OL,11,FJustice Minister, Alex Davies-Jones MP
OL,12,Fsaid: "The renters right act is a
OL,13,Flandmark bill and one I am very proud
OL,14,Fto have delivered in government to
OL,15,Fensure that we can get renters the
OL,16,Frights that they have so desperately
OL,17,Fneeded for so long. We are rebalancing
OL,18,Fthe situation between these landlords
OL,19,Fand the renters."
OL,26,@tD@GOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FBen Beadle from the National
OL,8,FResidential Landlords Association
OL,9,Ffeels as though the changes aren't a
OL,10,Fgood thing for landlords.
OL,12,FHe said: "We will have longer notice
OL,13,Fperiods and we will be at the behest
OL,14,Fof the court system. It takes on
OL,15,Faverage currently around eight months
OL,16,Fwith possession claims and that is
OL,17,Fonly going to increase."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/8
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,356,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1778073066
OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,FAs part of the changes, tenants now
OL,8,Fhave stronger rights for their pets
OL,9,Fand an end to bidding wars with prices
OL,10,Fhaving to be set at the advertised
OL,11,Frate.
OL,13,FProperty legal expert, Manjinder Kaur
OL,14,FAtwal said: "Ending the no fault
OL,15,Feviction would change the fundamental
OL,16,Frelationship between a landlord and a
OL,17,Ftenant.
OL,26,@vD@MOU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/8
