OL,3,C'I was devastated' - woman served
OL,4,Ceviction notice days before law takes
OL,5,Ceffect
OL,7,F"It would create stability and
OL,8,Fpredictability. Security isn't just
OL,9,Fabout evictions but it is also about
OL,10,Fhouse and conditions."
OL,12,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,13,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,14,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,15,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,16,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,17,Fbelow...
